SUMMARY:NIS Fall 2026 Poster Session
DTSTAMP:20260623T142735Z
DTSTART:20260922T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:For non-Rice attendees\, the nearest visitor lot is the North A
	nnex Lot (Alumni@Campanile). Enter campus at entrance 20 (Kent@Rice)\, and
	 turn right at the stop sign into the lot. Parking is credit/debit card on
	ly and costs $1 every 10 minutes for a daily maximum of $12. Space Science
	 is not the corner building\, but the building next to it with a loading d
	ock. The elevator and stairs are to the left of the dock. Once on the thir
	d floor\, turn right\, down the hall\, then left. Room 300 will be on the 
